#. <section class="sutta" id="an11.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an11.4:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 11"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 11"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an11.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Nissayavagga"
msgstr "1. Dependence"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an11.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyaupanisāsutta"
msgstr "4. Vital Conditions (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.315"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an11.4:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Venerable Sāriputta addressed the mendicants …"

#. VAR: bhikkhave”ti → bhikkhavoti (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an11.4:1.2"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti."
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an11.4:1.3"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "an11.4:1.4"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca:"
msgstr "Sāriputta said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an11.4:2.1"
msgid "“Dussīlassa, āvuso, sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro, "
msgstr ""
"“An unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a vital condition for "
"not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.2"
msgid "avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition "
"for joy. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.3"
msgid "pāmojje asati pāmojjavipannassa hatūpanisā hoti pīti, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no joy, one who lacks joy has destroyed a vital condition for "
"rapture. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.4"
msgid "pītiyā asati pītivipannassa hatūpanisā hoti passaddhi, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no rapture, one who lacks rapture has destroyed a vital "
"condition for tranquility. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.5"
msgid "passaddhiyā asati passaddhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti sukhaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no tranquility, one who lacks tranquility has destroyed a "
"vital condition for bliss. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.6"
msgid "sukhe asati sukhavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no bliss, one who lacks bliss has destroyed a vital condition "
"for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.7"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has "
"destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.8"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpanisā hoti "
"nibbidā, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and "
"vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.9"
msgid "nibbidāya asati nibbidāvipannassa hatūpaniso hoti virāgo, "
msgstr ""
"When there is no disillusionment, one who lacks disillusionment has "
"destroyed a vital condition for dispassion. "

msgctxt "an11.4:2.10"
msgid "virāge asati virāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is no dispassion, one who lacks dispassion has destroyed a vital "
"condition for knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an11.4:3.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, "
"softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an11.4:3.2"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, dussīlassa sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro, "
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a "
"vital condition for having no regrets. "

msgctxt "an11.4:3.3"
msgid ""
"avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition "
"for joy. …"

msgctxt "an11.4:3.4"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition "
"for knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.316"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an11.4:4.1"
msgid "Sīlavato, āvuso, sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro, "
msgstr ""
"An ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled a vital condition "
"for not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.2"
msgid ""
"avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for joy. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.3"
msgid "pāmojje sati pāmojjasampannassa upanisasampannā hoti pīti, "
msgstr ""
"When there is joy, one who has fulfilled joy has fulfilled a vital condition "
"for rapture. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.4"
msgid "pītiyā sati pītisampannassa upanisasampannā hoti passaddhi, "
msgstr ""
"When there is rapture, one who has fulfilled rapture has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for tranquility. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.5"
msgid "passaddhiyā sati passaddhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti sukhaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there is tranquility, one who has fulfilled tranquility has fulfilled a "
"vital condition for bliss. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.6"
msgid "sukhe sati sukhasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi, "
msgstr ""
"When there is bliss, one who has fulfilled bliss has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.7"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ, "
msgstr ""
"When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.8"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampannā "
"hoti nibbidā, "
msgstr ""
"When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true "
"knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.9"
msgid "nibbidāya sati nibbidāsampannassa upanisasampanno hoti virāgo, "
msgstr ""
"When there is disillusionment, one who has fulfilled disillusionment has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for dispassion. "

msgctxt "an11.4:4.10"
msgid ""
"virāge sati virāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is dispassion, one who has fulfilled dispassion has fulfilled a "
"vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an11.4:5.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its "
"shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an11.4:5.2"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, sīlavato sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti "
"avippaṭisāro, "
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled "
"a vital condition for not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an11.4:5.3"
msgid ""
"avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for joy. …"

msgctxt "an11.4:5.4"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti. … pe …"
msgstr ""
"One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for knowledge and vision of freedom.” …"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an11.4:5.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
